snippet: Nairo Quintana took the overall lead of the Vuelta a España from his Movistar teammate Alejandro Valverde after a rainy and mountainous ninth stage.
abstract: Winner Anacona wins ninth stage of Vuelta a Espana bicycle race; Nairo Quintana takes overall lead.
lead_paragraph: Nairo Quintana took the overall lead of the Vuelta a España from his Movistar teammate Alejandro Valverde after a rainy and mountainous ninth stage.

headline.main: Quintana Takes Lead After Rainy Vuelta Stage
